  "active_lock_reason": "resolved",
  "body": "Proposal: when compiling the contracts, hardhat should look for the path alias defined in remappings.txt, and replace the path as defined in the solidity [docs](https://docs.soliditylang.org/en/v0.8.17/path-resolution.html#import-remapping)\r\n\r\na simple example,\r\n\r\n`remappings.txt`:\r\n```txt\r\n@sample-project/=\"./sample-project/contracts/\"\r\n```\r\nand in the contracts:\r\n```solidity\r\nimport \"@sample-project/sample-contract.sol\"",
